After checkout :

codir = directory you've checked out to

- cd codir/axlv2
- make
- cd ..
- mkdir runs
- cd runs
- mkdir "nameofrun" : nameofrun can be any name, e.g. "testrun" or "2005105_1h" for a run of the 105th day of the year 2005 in a 1h timeresolution.
- cd "nameofrun"
- cp ../../axlv2/tools/run-axlv2-many.pl ./
- cp ../../axlv2/tools/axlv2.in ./

modify if necessary axlv2.in (you have a whole bunch of parameter that can be set)

create a shellfile :
e.g. run_2005105_1h.sh
"
./run-axlv2-many.pl 2005105 --accum=1h --config_file='axlv2.in'
"
(for more information about how to use run-axlv2-many.pl, call ./run-axlv2-many.pl -help)

execute shellfile

done!